source.name: USCIS National Processing Volumes and Trends
source.description: The dataset provides the public with a comparison of form processing volumes and trend data for specific form types and offices with national levels. This gives the public insight into the volume of forms USCIS is processing at each office, the status of those forms, and comparison to how USCIS processes nationally.
